br/></li>\n<li>赠我一场病 又慢慢痊愈摇风铃<br/></li>\n<li>赠我一场空 又渐渐填满真感情<br/></li>\n</ul>\n", "last_modified": 1740274430, "replies": 45, "id": 1113521}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 65893, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9241, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 175521, "username": "matthewzhong", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/matthewzhong", "website": "https://startpage.site/", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "广州市", "tagline": "Life is Short Programming More", "bio": "我的博客 blog.mzh.ren", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d65d/3436/175521_mini.png?m=1678928900", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d65d/3436/175521_normal.png?m=1678928900", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d65d/3436/175521_large.png?m=1678928900", "created": 1464756005, "last_modified": 1678928900}, "last_reply_by": "mumbler", "last_touched": 1740252203, "title": "驳《人工智能正在催生一代文盲程序员》", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1113431", "created": 1740191924, "deleted": 0, "content": "[驳《人工智能正在催生一代文盲程序员》]( https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/-m-ITkVRu2ShxkxELIBDKA)\r\n\r\n## 什么是文盲程序员？\r\n\r\n企业注重的是效率，只看结果，而不在乎你的代码是手搓的还是 AI 生成的。现在很多企业大量裁员，要求员工必须使用 AI ，不会用 AI 的就会被优化。\r\n\r\n而作为信息行业的程序员，更不应该视“手搓”为高级，AI 为低级。你连基础的工具都不会用，还谈什么高级？\r\n\r\n所以，**什么是文盲程序员？恰恰是不会用 AI 的程序员。**\r\n\r\n最后我想说，AI 不仅不会造就文盲程序员，反而会整体拉高程序员的水平。", "content_rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/-m-ITkVRu2ShxkxELIBDKA\" rel=\"nofollow\">驳《人工智能正在催生一代文盲程序员》</a></p>\n<h2>什么是文盲程序员？</h2>\n<p>企业注重的是效率，只看结果，而不在乎你的代码是手搓的还是 AI 生成的。现在很多企业大量裁员，要求员工必须使用 AI ，不会用 AI 的就会被优化。</p>\n<p>而作为信息行业的程序员，更不应该视“手搓”为高级，AI 为低级。你连基础的工具都不会用，还谈什么高级？</p>\n<p>所以，<strong>什么是文盲程序员？恰恰是不会用 AI 的程序员。</strong></p>\n<p>最后我想说，AI 不仅不会造就文盲程序员，反而会整体拉高程序员的水平。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1740191924, "replies": 43, "id": 1113431}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1630643991", "name": "iphone", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1630643991", "title": "iPhone", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone", "topics": 12090, "footer": "这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。", "header": "Say hello to the future.", "title_alternative": "iPhone", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991", "stars": 3477, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 8, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"id": 505234, "username": "Liuour", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Liuour", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c2f08034d77b6101eebb96ffa9eaea34?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c2f08034d77b6101eebb96ffa9eaea34?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c2f08034d77b6101eebb96ffa9eaea34?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1598260752, "last_modified": 1740194150}, "last_reply_by": "Mixx", "last_touched": 1740236757, "title": "掉进马桶的 iPhone ，换新手机的决心", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1113441", "created": 1740194395, "deleted": 0, "content": "昨晚经历了人生中最惨的一刻——我的 iPhone 跌进了马桶。虽然已经洗干净了，但心理阴影太大，手机已经不再是我曾经认识的那个它了。大概是时候考虑换新机了，毕竟，心理上的“水”也不太好清除… \r\n\r\n从马桶里取出手机后，直接用水龙头冲洗听筒和底部麦克风位置，结果导致内部进水，摄像头出现起雾。不过，好在系统、屏幕等一切都正常。\r\n![]( https://i.imgur.com/KTZl2tN.jpg)\r\n![]( https://i.imgur.com/3GeYcdj.jpg)", "content_rendered": "<p>昨晚经历了人生中最惨的一刻——我的 iPhone 跌进了马桶。虽然已经洗干净了，但心理阴影太大，手机已经不再是我曾经认识的那个它了。大概是时候考虑换新机了，毕竟，心理上的“水”也不太好清除… </p>\n<p>从马桶里取出手机后，直接用水龙头冲洗听筒和底部麦克风位置，结果导致内部进水，摄像头出现起雾。不过，好在系统、屏幕等一切都正常。\n<img alt=\"\"